productReviews.reviewText: My co-worker Kazuo has one of these. He says it looks transparent.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This calculating keeps them away.
My gentoo penguin loves to play with it.
The box this comes in is 3 yard by 6 light-year and weights 11 megaton!!
It only works when I'm Samoa.
